import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { useIntl } from "react-intl"; export default function ReturnSummaryInformation({salesReturnProposalSummary,totalSalesReturnProposalAmount,totalSalesReturnAmount,totalReturnQuantity}) { const intl = useIntl(); return ( <>
{salesReturnProposalSummary.invoiceNo}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.RETURN_INVOICE_NO"})} 		{salesReturnProposalSummary.invoiceDate}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.RETURN_INVOICE_DATE"})}
{salesReturnProposalSummary.invoiceAmount}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.RETURN_INVOICE_AMOUNT"})}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "COMMON.FISCAL_YEAR"})}
{salesReturnProposalSummary.salesReturnNo}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.RETURN_NO"})} 		{salesReturnProposalSummary.proposalNo}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.RETURN_PROPOSAL_NO"})}
{salesReturnProposalSummary.salesReturnDate}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.RETURN_DATE"})} 		{salesReturnProposalSummary.proposalDate}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "COMMON.PROPOSAL_DATE"})}
{totalReturnQuantity}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.RETURN_QTY"})} 		{salesReturnProposalSummary.totalQuantity}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.PROPOSE_QTY"})}
{totalSalesReturnAmount}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.AMOUNT"})} 		{totalSalesReturnProposalAmount}
{intl.formatMessage({id: "SALES.RETURN.PROPOSAL.AMOUNT"})}
); }
